column5: What a awesome day to spend on the water, even better when your catching these
Very nice! Its a shame about keeping those females with all those eggs, but it amazes me how it doesn't even put a dent in the perch fishery.
On Erie if the dent is coming from anywhere its the commercial fishery
Those are the biggest perch I have ever seen. Way to go.
Those are some fat hogs man.
I was just about to post the exact same thing..
Very NIce!  Were the fish in shallow or were you guys still out in deeper water>?
Obviously smallies with killer paint jobs....  Looks to be the biggest I've ever seen.
I even like the colors! Pike and skis do too!
WHAT!!????!?!? HOLY!!! those are some HUGE PERCH MAN!!!! AMAZING!!!!

I fished Erie this weekend also kept 25 perch all were spawned out except 1 little male that was hooked deep not 1 of the big girls had eggs left and fish were being caught from 18 to 55 FOW. BTW those are huge perch makes the 13"ers I caught tiny
Almost all the big fish were spawned out...
Nice perch, must be nice to live near such a great fishery!
Upper Niagara River & Lake Erie the Best!
